{"id":6545,"date":"2023-05-22T05:21:00","date_gmt":"2023-05-22T05:21:00","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/sman1bdg.sch.id\/?p=6545"},"modified":"2023-05-23T05:23:20","modified_gmt":"2023-05-23T05:23:20","slug":"smansa-1990-salurkan-bantuan-bencana-alam-pohon-tumbang-di-sekolah","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/sman1bdg.sch.id\/2023\/05\/22\/smansa-1990-salurkan-bantuan-bencana-alam-pohon-tumbang-di-sekolah\/","title":{"rendered":"SMANSA 1990 Salurkan Bantuan Bencana Alam Pohon Tumbang di Sekolah"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Alumni SMANSA Angkatan 1990 salurkan bantuan bencana alam pohon tumbanh di sekolah.<br>Ibu kepala SMAN 1 Bandung Tuti Kurniawati menerima tamu perwakilan SMANSA 90 untuk menerima bantuan.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>SMA Negeri 1 Bandung kondisi saat ini sedang tetimpa musibah pohon tumbang beberapa minggu kebelakang. Akibatnya sejumlah bangunan rusak parah.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Alumni SMANSA Angkatan 1990 salurkan bantuan bencana alam pohon tumbanh di sekolah.Ibu kepala SMAN 1 Bandung Tuti Kurniawati menerima tamu perwakilan SMANSA 90 untuk menerima bantuan. SMA Negeri 1 Bandung kondisi saat ini sedang tetimpa musibah pohon tumbang beberapa minggu kebelakang. Akibatnya sejumlah bangunan rusak parah.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":6546,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[9],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/sman1bdg.sch.id\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/6545"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/sman1bdg.sch.id\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/sman1bdg.sch.id\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sman1bdg.sch.id\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sman1bdg.sch.id\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=6545"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/sman1bdg.sch.id\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/6545\/r